<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3573462>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Tanaidaceans species of the sublittoral zone of the northern Yucatan Peninsula, suborder Apseudomorpha. (A) Mesokalliapseudes macsweenyi ♂; (B) M. macsweenyi ♀; (C) Psammokalliapseudes granulosus ♂; (D) P. granulosus ♀; (E) Calozodion wadei ♂; (F) C. wadei ♀; (G) Pagurotanais largoensis ♂; (H) Shells that P. largoensis inhabits: upper left, Eulithidium affine; upper right, Zebina browniana; lower left, Cerithium eburneum; lower right, Stellatoma stellata." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3573462/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3573460>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Diversity, abundance, and distribution of tanaidaceans of the sublittoral zone of the northern Yucatan Peninsula." ;
